Node.Caption: C01SkjorEntry

Cell.Text: This is a simple errand, but the time is right for it to be your Trial. Carry yourself with honor, and you'll become a true Companion.

Node.Caption: C01SkjorWhyMeTopic: What does this have to do with me?

Cell.Text: There's a fine line between respect and boot-licking, new blood. But I like your spirit. | We've decided this will be your Trial. Do well, and you'll be counted among the Companions.

Node.Caption: C01SkjorPickMePickMeBranchTopic: I would be honored to retrieve it.

Cell.Text: Wuuthrad was the blade held by Ysgramor when he cut through the elven hordes that once swarmed this land. | He made it safe for our kind.
Wuuthrad was the blade held by Ysgramor when he came back from Atmora. | An axe of great vengeance. Each fragment is precious.
